### 1. Get My Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/my-transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get My Transactions with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/my-transactions?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Transaction Summary (Total, Last Month, Balance)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Transactions Filtered by Type (Earnings only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/my-transactions?type=earning
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Transactions Filtered by Status (Completed only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/my-transactions?status=completed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get Transactions with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/my-transactions?dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

